On First Take, Stephen A. Smith, Damien Woody and Louis Riddick react to Shedeur Sanders falling to the 5th round of the NFL Draft and being selected by the Cleveland Browns.

snippet.title: Shedeur Sanders sliding is HIS OWN FAULT, Seahawks WIN BIG in 2025 NFL Draft | Colin Cowherd Podcast
snippet.description:
Colinâ€™s joined by John Middlekauff, host of â€œ3 and Outâ€ to recap the 2025 NFL Draft! They dissect the saga of Shedeur Sanders, why he turned off so many teams, and why the Browns selecting him feels like an â€œownership pick.â€ They discuss why it was a â€œstarter draftâ€ not a â€œstarâ€ draft, why the Jaguars were completely fleeced for Travis Hunter, and why intelligence is the most important trait in a prospect. Finally they point to the Seahawks as the winners of the draft, debate whether the Rams had eyes on QB Jaxson Dart, and break down why Texas QB Quinn Ewers went from a first round prospect to seventh round selection.

0:00 Shedeur Sanders storyline
2:15 If a quarterback isnâ€™t the starter, teams donâ€™t want to deal with â€œnoiseâ€
4:30 Shedeur turned teams off in predraft meetings
8:00 Quarterbacks are held to a higher standard

snippet.title: The Most Dangerous Building in Manhattan
snippet.description:
How a single phone call from a student helped uncover a flaw that nearly toppled Citicorp. Get an exclusive 15% discount on Saily data plans! Use code veritasium at checkout. Download Saily app or go to https://saily.com/veritasium 

If youâ€™re looking for a molecular modeling kit, try Snatoms, a kit I invented where the atoms snap together magnetically - https://ve42.co/SnatomsV 

Note: From construction images of Citicorp, sharp-eyed viewers might see that the mid-V columns are still there. Those columns help prevent buckling of the diagonal and the weight of people on the floor above, but do not take the majority of the gravity load. So we left them out of our diagram to clearly explain the load paths. See page 70 of this source for more details - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ODFo66-_V7Y9vKANbj53mQ0z20RZ2Uai/view

â–€â–€â–€
0:00 Why is the citicorp building on stilts?
4:44 How wind load works
7:49 Tuned Mass Dampers 
11:17 The Anonymous Student
14:00 Quartering Winds
18:38 What were the odds of collapse?
20:31 How was the citicorp building fixed?
25:40 Hurricane Ella
27:00 TMDs Take Over The World
28:36 Conspiracies and Cover Ups

â–€â–€â–€
A big thank you for the incredible people without whom we couldn't have done this! ğŸ–¤

To Michael Greenburg, author of The Great Miscalculation, for his insights that really brought the story and its context to life. He gave us a pre-copy of his upcoming book, and it is fantastic: https://ve42.co/Miscalc
To Eric Hines for all his help with the technical details, fact-checking, and making sure we got the engineering right.

To Michael J. Vardaro for helping us uncover the details of the story and the resources he provided. 
To Brock Hedegaard for helping us dive deep into the Citicorp structural analysis. Learn the fundamentals of structural analysis on his brilliant channel: https://www.youtube.com/@StructuresProfH/videos
To Michele Barbato from UC Davis for his inputs on the load calculations.
https://faculty.engineering.ucdavis.edu/barbato/

To Prof. Chris Letchford who helped us understand the impact of wind on Citicorp's structure. 
To DongHun Yeo from NIST for discussing his research about wind effects on buildings similar to citicorp: https://ve42.co/WindLoad

Finally, to Team Columbia â€”who built the epic TMD and ran wind tunnel experiments that made this story come alive.
This includes the folks at the Mechanical Engineering Teaching Laboratory
(Follow all the cool stuff theyâ€™re doing: @mechcu, @columbiaengineering or visit https://teachinglab.me/)
Amanda Lombardo, Manager of Instructional Laboratories
Daniela DurÃ³n GarcÃ­a, Assistant Manager of Instructional Laboratories
Jorge Casas, Machinist
And the amazing seniors from the Columbia Space Initiative:
(Support their awesome work here: columbiaspace.org/support-us/, Follow them: @columbiaspaceinitiative)
Michael Sheehan
Claudio Solano
Jessica Bolar
Kathryn Lampo

â–€â–€â–€
References:
Michael M. Greenburg. The Great Miscalculation via. nyupress.org - https://ve42.co/Miscalc
Joe Morgenstern. The Fifty-Nine-Story Crisis via. The New Yorker - https://ve42.co/59Crisis
National Academy of Engineering. William LeMessurier-The Fifty-Nine-Story Crisis: A Lesson in Professional Behavior - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=um-7IlAdAtg
Diane Lee Hartley. Implications of a Major Urban Office Complex: The Scientific, Social and Symbolic Meanings of Citicorp Center via. princeton.edu - https://ve42.co/CitiSymbol
Caroline Whitbeck. William LeMessurier: The Fifty-Nine-Story Crisis, A Lesson in Professional Behavior via.  Online Ethics - https://ve42.co/BillCrisis
Addition References here: https://ve42.co/citiref

â–€â–€â–€
Special thanks to our Patreon supporters:
Adam Foreman, Albert Wenger, Alex Porter, Alexander Tamas, Anton Ragin, Autodidactic Studios, Balkrishna Heroor, Bertrand Serlet, Blake Byers, Bruce, Dave Kircher, David Johnston, David Tseng, Evgeny Skvortsov, Garrett Mueller, Gnare, gpoly, Greg Scopel, HydrochloRick, Jon Jamison, Juan Benet, Keith England, KeyWestr, Kyi, Lee Redden, Marinus Kuivenhoven, Matthias Wrobel, Meekay, meg noah, Michael Krugman, Orlando Bassotto, Paul Peijzel, Richard Sundvall, Sam Lutfi, Tj Steyn, TTST, Ubiquity Ventures, wolfee

snippet.title: My best competition in YEARS
snippet.description:
Get a FREE 8g MagLock Non-Chalk (silica-based grip enhancer) with any order over $100 USD. Use code FREEMAGLOCK  â–¶ï¸ https://rungne.com

Disclaimer:
Maglock contains amorphous silica silicate, which differs significantly from crystalline silica associated with silicosis and other lung conditions. While amorphous silica is generally considered safe and rapidly dissolves if inhaled, prolonged inhalation of any dust particles should always be avoided. We recommend using Maglock responsibly: Minimize airborne dust, use in well-ventilated areas, and avoid deliberate inhalation. 

My best competition in YEARS - Magnus MidtbÃ¸

Shot and Edited by Sam Tuck https://www.instagram.com/samtuclimbing 

Music and Sound Effects: http://share.epidemicsound.com/vSnfn

snippet.title: I Connected My Three Giant Vivariums Together and It Changed Everything
snippet.description:
I finally connected my three giant ecosystem vivariums together, and the result was unbelievable. My long term plan had come to completion when my rainforest floor vivarium, canopy vivarium, and tropical wetlands vivarium became a single space, with shared animals freely able to cross over to the different habitats. I was shocked at what animals crossed over through the new cave tunnel bridge. Our rainforest ecosystem within glass has been forever changed. Hope you enjoy the Season 4 Finale of my Ecosystem Vivarium Series. Ant love forever! This video was shot in 4K Ultra HD resolution.

id.title: Saya Menyambungkan Tiga Vivarium Raksasa Saya dan Itu Mengubah Segalanya
id.description:
Akhirnya saya menghubungkan tiga vivarium ekosistem raksasa saya bersama-sama, dan hasilnya sungguh luar biasa. Rencana jangka panjang saya telah selesai ketika vivarium lantai hutan hujan, vivarium kanopi, dan vivarium lahan basah tropis saya menjadi satu ruang, dengan hewan-hewan yang digunakan bersama dapat dengan bebas menyeberang ke habitat yang berbeda. Saya terkejut melihat hewan-hewan apa saja yang menyeberang melalui jembatan terowongan gua yang baru. Ekosistem hutan hujan kita di dalam kaca telah berubah selamanya. Semoga Anda menikmati Final Musim ke-4 dari Seri Vivarium Ekosistem saya. Cinta semut selamanya! Video ini direkam dalam resolusi 4K Ultra HD. it.title: Ho collegato i miei tre terrari giganti e tutto Ã¨ cambiato
it.description:
Ho finalmente collegato i miei tre giganteschi vivari ecosistemici e il risultato Ã¨ stato incredibile. Il mio piano a lungo termine si Ã¨ concluso quando il mio vivario sul suolo della foresta pluviale, il vivario sulla volta e il vivario delle zone umide tropicali sono diventati un unico spazio, con animali condivisi in grado di attraversare liberamente i diversi habitat. Sono rimasto scioccato da quali animali siano riusciti a passare attraverso il nuovo ponte a tunnel nella grotta. Il nostro ecosistema della foresta pluviale in vetro Ã¨ cambiato per sempre. Spero che vi piaccia il finale della quarta stagione della mia serie "Vivarium Ecosistemici". Amore per le formiche per sempre! Questo video Ã¨ stato girato in risoluzione 4K Ultra HD. en.title: I Connected My Three Giant Vivariums Together and It Changed Everything
en.description:
I finally connected my three giant ecosystem vivariums together, and the result was unbelievable. My long term plan had come to completion when my rainforest floor vivarium, canopy vivarium, and tropical wetlands vivarium became a single space, with shared animals freely able to cross over to the different habitats. I was shocked at what animals crossed over through the new cave tunnel bridge. Our rainforest ecosystem within glass has been forever changed. Hope you enjoy the Season 4 Finale of my Ecosystem Vivarium Series. Ant love forever! This video was shot in 4K Ultra HD resolution.

snippet.title: Trump border czar Tom Homan on U.S. children removed from country during deportations
snippet.description:
Trump administration border czar Tom Homan argued on "Face the Nation" that when someone enters the country illegally and chooses to have a child, automatically granting the child American citizenship, "that's on you, that's not on this administration." Homan made the statement when asked about the three children who are American citizens who were removed Friday with their mothers from the U.S. to Honduras, according to court documents reviewed by CBS News.

#trump #politics #news

The broadcast is one of the longest-running news programs in the history of television, having debuted November 7, 1954, on CBS. Trump administration border czar Tom Homan argued on "Face the Nation" that when someone enters the country illegally and chooses to have a child, automatically granting the child American citizenship, "that's on you, that's not on this administration." Homan made the statement when asked about the three children who are American citizens who were removed Friday with their mothers from the U.S. to Honduras, according to court documents reviewed by CBS News.

#trump #politics #news 

"Face the Nation" is America's premier Sunday morning public affairs program. The broadcast is one of the longest-running news programs in the history of television, having debuted November 7, 1954, on CBS. Every Sunday, "Face the Nation" moderator and CBS News senior foreign affairs correspondent Margaret Brennan welcomes leaders, newsmakers, and experts to a lively round table discussion of current events and the latest news.

snippet.title: I Spent 24 Hours at the World's Largest Hotel
snippet.description:
Thanks to Saily for sponsoring this video!! Get an exclusive 15% discount on Saily data plans by using code â€œSAFIYAâ€ at checkout. Download the Saily app or go to https://saily.com/safiya ğŸ•ºğŸ»

HELLO FRIENDS!! And welcome to another video!! For years, Tyler and I have dreamt about visiting the Worldâ€™s Largest Hotel, located all the way in the Genting Highlands, Malaysia - and to conclude our trip to Southeast Asia last summer (where we pulled All-Nighter in Singapore, spent 24 hours at Singaporeâ€™s Changi Airport, and ate at the famed Malaysian night market Jalan Alor), we headed into the mountains to spend 24 hours at the First World Hotel.

From their indoor AND outdoor theme park(s), to their celebrity chef restaurants, scenic views, Ice Age roller coasters and questionable towels, it was certainly a whirlwind 24 hours. What did you guys think? Would you visit this hotel? And where should we go next?

id.description:
Terima kasih kepada Saily yang telah mensponsori video ini!! Dapatkan diskon eksklusif 15% untuk paket data Saily dengan menggunakan kode â€œSAFIYAâ€ saat pembayaran. Unduh aplikasi Saily atau kunjungi https://saily.com/safiya ğŸ•ºğŸ»

HALO TEMAN-TEMAN!! Dan selamat datang di video lainnya!! Selama bertahun-tahun, Tyler dan saya bermimpi untuk mengunjungi Hotel Terbesar di Dunia, yang terletak di Genting Highlands, Malaysia - dan untuk mengakhiri perjalanan kami ke Asia Tenggara musim panas lalu (di mana kami begadang semalaman di Singapura, menghabiskan 24 jam di Bandara Changi Singapura, dan makan di pasar malam Malaysia yang terkenal, Jalan Alor), kami menuju ke pegunungan untuk menghabiskan 24 jam di First World Hotel.

Dari taman hiburan dalam DAN luar ruangan, hingga restoran koki selebriti, pemandangan indah, roller coaster Ice Age, dan handuk yang meragukan, itu benar-benar 24 jam yang luar biasa. id.title: Reaksi terhadap Shedeur Sanders yang direkrut oleh Cleveland Browns dalam NFL Draft | Podcast Col...
id.description:
Colin bereaksi terhadap kekalahan Shedeur Sanders dalam draft NFL dan Cleveland Browns yang akhirnya memilihnya di ronde ke-5. Ia menjelaskan mengapa Shedeur bukanlah prospek yang cukup baik untuk mengatasi kerumunan di sekitarnya, mengapa kesombongan ayahnya Deion merusak reputasinya dalam draft, dan mengapa tim NFL tidak menginginkan "quarterback selebriti" sebagai pemain cadangan mereka. Timeline
0:00 Kesombongan Deion tidak membantu saham draft Shedeur
2:00 Shedeur bukanlah prospek yang cukup baik untuk menuntut tim NFL
3:45 "Ayah Quarterback" menjadi "Ibu Pageant" dan menyakiti anak itu
5:00 Beberapa tim melaporkan bahwa Shedeur buruk dalam rapat dan tidak terlibat
6:30 Kedewasaan dan fokus lebih penting bagi quarterback
9:45 Ruang quarterback Cleveland berantakan
11:15 Shedeur adalah prospek yang bagus, bukan yang hebat
13:00 Tim tidak menginginkan "QB selebriti" sebagai cadangan mereka

snippet.title: President Donald Trump arrives in Rome with Melania Trump for Pope Francis' funeral in Vatican City
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump flew to Rome aboard Air Force One to attend the funeral for Pope Francis. The Trumps are expected to depart Italy some time Saturday night.

00:00 - Air Force One lands at Rome airport with Melania and Donald Trump
13:23 - Melania and Donald Trump deplane Air Force One in Italy
16:35 - Melania and Donald Trump depart airport in Rome
20:20 - Air Force One sits on Leonardo da Vinci International Airport runway

snippet.title: Exclusive: Young Thug Speaks on New Album and Life After Jail | The GQ Video Cover Story
snippet.description:
â€œI love people so much to the point that, the only thing that will make me not love you anymore is betrayal,â€ says Young Thug as he towers over _GQâ€™s_ Zach Baron in a perfectly landscaped garden, which sits next to an eccentric taxidermy-filled mansion on the East Side of Los Angeles.

In October of last year, the rapper Young Thug walked free from the Fulton County jail in Atlanta, concluding one of the strangest and most fraught spectacles in modern music. In May 2022 as part of a complex RICO case, Georgia prosecutors alleged that Young Thugâ€”in addition to being the head of a record label, YSLâ€”was also the leader of a gang of the same name. What followed was the longest criminal trial in Georgia history. 

Since getting out, Young Thug has mostly laid low, to the point of sometimes wearing a mask in public. He has not said much about the last few years of his life, or about anything at all, reallyâ€¦ until now. This is the _GQ_ Video Covery Story with Young Thug.

snippet.title: Donald Trump departs DC for Pope Francis' funeral aboard Air Force One with first lady Melania Trump
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump boarded Air Force One together at Joint Base Andrews in Maryland on Friday, April 25, 2025, to fly to Rome. The presidential couple will be attending the funeral processions in Vatican City for Pope Francis.

00:00 - Melania and Donald Trump arrive at Joint Base Andrews aboard Marine One
05:53 - Donald Trump boards Air Force One with Melania Trump
08:00 - Air Force One prepares to fly Melania and Donald Trump to Italy
11:51 - Melania and Donald Trump take off on Air Force One for Pope Francis funeral

snippet.title: Grupo Frontera: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
Anamaria Sayre | April 24, 2025
Grupo Frontera, which was headlining backyard bailes well before stadium shows, feels perfectly made for Tiny Desk. Beneath the glow of fluorescent office lights and backed against trinket-stuffed shelves, the match feels divinely ordained.

Normally, jazzy vocal trills and norteÃ±o cumbia rhythms are star-crossed lovers, but not at the Tiny Desk. At the center of a pop-infused reinvigoration of traditional Mexican sounds, the members of Grupo Frontera are masters of unlikely pairings. Mega-producer and songwriter Edgar Barrera discovered Grupo Frontera at a quinceanera in his hometown, enthralled by the band's authenticity. He encouraged the band's Texas-bred beats, killer melodies and contemporary lyrics.

There's no better space to highlight the impressive musicality of the group and stunning vocals of Payo Solis than in a stripped down setting. "Yo nacÃ­ pa' querer a la que no me quiere (I was born to love the one who doesn't love me)," Payo coos. But it's hard to feel heartbroken when desamor sounds so smooth.

snippet.title: After Pope Francis, what happens next? | ABC NEWS
snippet.description:
Following the passing of Pope Francis, a strict set of rules and protocols is set into motion, guiding the transition to the next Pope. This tradition traces its origins back to Saint Peterâ€”the first Popeâ€”believed to have been chosen by Jesus himself. 
Subscribe: http://ab.co/1svxLVE
Read more here: https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-04-21/pope-francis-dies-catholic-church-vatican/103550594
Over the centuries, generations of Catholic leaders have refined the process into a meticulously choreographed and deeply internalized election. Ultimately, the Cardinals select one of their own to ascend as the moral and spiritual leader of the Catholic Church.

snippet.title: Police give latest update on car attack at festival in Vancouver
snippet.description:
At least 11 people have been killed and several others injured after a vehicle struck a crowd at a street festival in Vancouver, according to police.

Deputy chief constable Steve Rai of the Vancouver Police Department provided an update, revealing that the alleged driver has a history of interactions with both law enforcement and healthcare professionals.

He also stated: "While I'm confident the joint risk assessment and public safety plan was sound, we will be working with our partners at the city of Vancouver to review all of the circumstances surrounding the planning of this event."

Read more: https://news.sky.com/story/several-killed-after-vehicle-drives-into-crowd-at-street-festival-police-in-vancouver-say-13356722

snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Elena Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Bringing a pawsitive attitude and capoeira style, Elena charges in to Street Fighter 6 on June 5 as the final character from Year 2!

With a herd of fluid moves that will turn any opponent into prey, Elena promises each fight will be elephantastic.

Elena can be purchased individually with Fighter Coins and the owners of the Year 2 Character Pass / Ultimate Pass or Years 1-2 Fighters Edition, will automatically get access to Elena when she releases.

Please note that depending on the timezone you reside in, Elena may release the day before on June 4 following server maintenance.

snippet.title: Loving Mother & Herd Do All They Can to Save Baby Buffalo from Lions
snippet.description:
When a hungry lion pride targeted a defenseless baby buffalo, things should have been over quickly. But, luckily, the very protective mother buffalo was still around and kept bashing the lions off her calf.
Not only that! The bravery of the mother buffalo gave the rest of the buffaloes the courage to come and join her rescue mission!

snippet.title: Letâ€™s talk: Therapy, GLP1 & The Truth About My recent Weight Loss
snippet.description: This isn't easy to say, but I owe it to you to be honest. Janelle Rohner is micro dosing a GLP-1. I've quietly been working on my mental health, trying to find peace in the chaos. I know sharing this might open me up to judgment, but hiding it would mean losing the most important thing: my truth. I'm not perfect, but l'm healing-and I hope that means something to someone out there who's struggling too.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls 4: Oblivion Remastered - 15 NEW Things You Need To Know Before You Buy
snippet.description:
Bethesda Softworks has finally announced what everyone has been buzzing about for weeks - The Elder Scrolls 4: Oblivion Remastered. Developed with Virtuos, the remaster features overhauled visuals made possible with Unreal Engine 5.

The character models, environments and other assets have been rebuilt from scratch. A new real-time lighting system allows for full dynamic shadows Cyrodiil, while the new lip-synching tech meshes well with the brand-new dialogue. Of course, there are also numerous quality-of-life improvements, from hit reactions in combat and an improved third-person perspective to sprinting and levelling changes.

The Elder Scrolls 4: Oblivion Remastered is out now on PS5, PC, and Xbox Series X/S for $49.99. You can also play it on Game Pass for PC, consoles, and the cloud, but here's what you should know before diving in.

-----------------------------------------------------------------
The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivionâ„¢ Remastered modernizes the 2006 Game of the Year with all new stunning visuals and refined gameplay. Explore the vast landscape of Cyrodiil like never before and stop the forces of Oblivion from overtaking the land in one of the greatest RPGs ever from the award-winning Bethesda Game Studios.

Rediscover Cyrodiil
Journey through the rich world of Tamriel and battle across the planes of Oblivion where handcrafted details have been meticulously recreated to ensure each moment of exploration is awe-inspiring.

Navigate Your Own Story
From the noble warrior to the sinister assassin, wizened sorcerer, or scrappy blacksmith, forge your path and play the way you want.

Experience an Epic Adventure
Step inside a universe bursting with captivating stories and encounter an unforgettable cast of characters. Master swordcraft and wield powerful magic as you fight to save Tamriel from the Daedric invasion.

The Complete Story
Experience everything Oblivion has to offer with previously released story expansions Shivering Isles, Knights of the Nine, and additional downloadable content included in The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered.
~ Official Description

The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered | Official Details

â–«ï¸ Rebuilt from the ground up in UE5 on top of Oblivion engine
â–«ï¸ Updated leveling system with some elements from Skyrim
â–«ï¸ Sprint added. Updated movement system.
â–«ï¸ New UI
â–«ï¸ Updated audio
â–«ï¸ Updated combat animations and gore
â–«ï¸ Recorded new lines of dialogue - each race now sounds unique
â–«ï¸ Includes all DLC expansions
â–«ï¸ Out now on PS5, PC, Xbox, and Xbox Game Pass

This is basically a remake!

Oblivion Remastered is quite literally a REMAKE.

Some major details:

- Gameplay touched up, new levelling system that's between Skyrim and Oblivion
- New voices added and new lines recorded
- All OG hilarious lines are back
- Fully remade visuals from the ground-up
- All animations remade
- Combat has been remade with a new dodge button
- You can now SPRINT!
- Unreal Engine 5 Visuals
- ALL DLCs are included

THIS IS AN INSANE PROJECT TO JUST SHADOWDROP, A HUGE DEA
